SHOW SYNOPSIS:
Home and Away (also commonly abbreviated in writing to H&A) is a Logie-winning soap opera that is produced in Sydney by the Seven Network since July 1987. It premiered on 17 January 1988 and is now one of the longest-running series on Australian television. The show initially focused on the characters of Pippa and Tom Fletcher who ran the Summer Bay Caravan Park and lived there with a succession of foster children, but the show has expanded and now explores the lives of various characters of Summer Bay.

EPISODE SUMMARY:
Annie and the Hospital attacker Rev. Hall are in a car praying, but is Annie in danger? Will Geoff & Roman get to them in time? Meanwhile, with two mean interested in her, who will Rachel choose, Roman or Tony?
